Hosting Ecommerce website using Cloud Front 

Steps to perform :
upload index.html and style.css file in s3 buckets.
S3 bucket settings.under Permissions, locate the Block public access settings.
Click Bucket Policy for cloudfront that specified in s3_policy_cloudfront
Navigate to cloudfront and create distribution policy 
under Origin sections perform below steps
  Set Origin Domain Name to your S3 bucket.
  Set Origin Access to Origin Access Control (OAC).
  Click Create Control Setting and attach it to your S3 bucket.
